            <title><![CDATA[中国网民齐夸露肩装是“最适合打疫苗的着装”]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<div class="figure-media figure-media-gallery figure-media-gallery-overlay js-figure-media-gallery js-figure-media-gallery-overlay">
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-04/%E6%BC%8F%E4%BB%B6.jpg?GjTWQ6akQvPXGmbVYD4tVW0cLLxyulFT&itok=QprmDP_L" alt data-caption src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-04/%E6%BC%8F%E4%BB%B6.jpg?GjTWQ6akQvPXGmbVYD4tVW0cLLxyulFT&itok=QprmDP_L" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
      <figcaption><p></p></figcaption>
  </div>
         <div class="figure-media-gallery-slide"><div class="figure-media-gallery-img"><img class="article-rotator-img lazyload" data-src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-04/%E6%BC%8F%E4%BB%B696lpj30ku0rs42f.jpg?Dwqu0vmg.yxe8lwxF8eJfIdMRg5ZuL55&itok=LVVZ9ytj" alt data-caption src="https://static.zaobao.com/s3fs-public/styles/article_large_full/public/2021-04/%E6%BC%8F%E4%BB%B696lpj30ku0rs42f.jpg?Dwqu0vmg.yxe8lwxF8eJfIdMRg5ZuL55&itok=LVVZ9ytj" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><div class="tint"></div></div>
